These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts, satire, disaster, western
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, trance, soul, blues, techno
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, havana, prince, oliveros, alhambra
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, bellflower, amaryllis, tulip, iris
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 2. the person who growsiris is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 5. the havana-smoker is the fan of blues##1
 6. the fan of trance is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of trance##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
11. the havana-smoker is the person who growsaconite##1
12. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts  | romance    | disaster | satire    | western  |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | jazz | soul | blues | techno  |
| Cigar           | montecristo     | alhambra     | oliveros  | havana   | prince    |
| Flower         | amaryllis | tulip    | bellflower | aconite  | iris |

