.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, ferret, goat, snake
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, woodworking, card-games, chess, filmmaking
House: tower, cape-cod, art-deco, palace, wooden
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, tea, water, milk
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the cape-cod house##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 4. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
 5. the wooden house is on the right of the palace house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the tower house##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is the art-deco house##1
 9. the person drinking water is the owner of the ferret##1
10. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
12. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Pet          | ferret        | snake | bird     | goat      | turtle  |
| Hobby           | woodworking   | card-games | filmmaking    | chess | camping |
| House   | art-deco | palace     | wooden | tower    | cape-cod  |
| Beverage   | water     | almond-milk | coffee    | milk      | tea    |

