House: colonial, palace, ranch-style, gothic-revival, farmhouse
5 different games are played: go, whist, backgammon, monopoly, mah-jongg
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the colonial house is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
 5. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the palace house##1
11. the ranch-style house is the owner of the lizard##1
12. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Sport      | climbing          | lacrosse  | biathlon       | rowing     | parkour      |
| Pet         | rat | frog | guinea-pig  | ferret   | lizard    |
| House   | palace        | farmhouse | colonial | gothic-revival    | ranch-style   |
| Game     | go   | backgammon | mah-jongg      | whist | monopoly |

