The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, november, september, august, october
The people have 5 different jobs:  musician, nurse, librarian, accountant, project-manager
 1. the colombian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 2. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is the colombian##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the italian##1
 5. the british is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
