 7. the nurse is on the right of the american##1
 8. the project-manager is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the musician is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby          | drawing        | fishing       | woodworking | photography   | baking  |
| Nationality   | american | british | colombian | italian   | german |
