 3. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is the person driving the train##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
12. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Pet         | pony  | fish  | rat    | rabbit | horse |
