5 different games are played: backgammon, chess, billiard, snooker, scrabble
 1. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is the person playing billiard##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes green is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
12. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
14. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
