.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, domino, go, backgammon
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, coral, green, azure, red
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea, amaryllis, orchid, rose
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, gardening, filmmaking, magic-tricks
 1. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 7. the person who likes coral is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person playing go##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who likes red##1
12. the person who likes green is the person who growsorchid##1
13. the person who likes red is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Game      | monopoly      | scrabble       | backgammon         | go  | domino |
| Color   | green  | azure | coral | ebony  | red  |
| Flower   | orchid    | azalea    | aconite        | rose | amaryllis     |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | gardening      | cooking       | filmmaking   | magic-tricks   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  coach, manager, musician, teacher, police-officer
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bolivar, chaman, pall-mall, prince
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, aconite, daisy, bellflower
5 different games are played: whist, backgammon, monopoly, poker, domino
 1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 4. the police-officer is on the left of the coach##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the police-officer##1
 7. the manager is the person playing whist##1
 8. the musician is the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
10. the person who growsorchid is the prince-smoker##1
11. the person playing poker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
12. the police-officer is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
13. the teacher is the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Job   | manager      | teacher | musician  | police-officer    | coach |
| Cigar   | pall-mall     | prince     | bolivar | dunhill      | chaman      |
| Flower           | aconite       | orchid     | begonia     | bellflower     | daisy   |
| Game         | whist | poker | backgammon  | domino | monopoly   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, siglo, cain, baccarat, game
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, amaryllis, iris, dahlia
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, crime, scientific, animation, disaster
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, dutch, american, japanese, russian
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the russian is on the right of the dutch##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is the thai##1
 4. the american is on the far right##1
 5. the dutch is the cain-smoker##1
 6. the russian is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the russian is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the thai is in the middle##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person who growsrose is on the left of the russian##1
12. the person who growsamaryllis is the game-smoker##1
13. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Cigar      | cain | game    | siglo   | baccarat   | davidoff |
| Flower   | rose    | amaryllis   | dahlia | iris | balloon-flower  |
| Movie-Genre           | crime     | animation | scientific   | disaster | family   |
| Nationality     | dutch  | russian   | thai    | japanese   | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, backgammon, bridge, domino
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bluemaster, dunhill, old-henry, ritmeester
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, golf, rowing, parkour
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, aquamarine, lavender, amber, apricot
 1. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
10. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
11. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is in the middle##1
13. the person who's sport is tennis is the person playing bridge##1
14. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Game      | poker | bridge   | backgammon    | mah-jongg       | domino |
| Cigar   | dunhill           | bluemaster   | ritmeester   | old-henry       | siglo  |
| Sport   | baseball       | tennis | golf | rowing     | parkour   |
| Color     | lavender    | aquamarine   | amber   | pink | apricot   |

 